<h2 class="bold font-l">Mother Hen Franklin</h2>
<p class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
Franklin wants to keep his little sister Harriet safe after she took a fall and scraped her knee during a wagon ride. But his attempts to make her playtime safe keep her from having any fun. </p>
</div>
